**使用迭代器进行正反向遍历：**

 `mp.begin()`和`mp.end()`用法：
**用于正向遍历map**

```cpp
map<int,int> mp;
mp[1] = 2;
mp[2] = 3;
mp[3] = 4;
auto it = mp.begin();
while(it != mp.end())
{
	cout << it->first << " " << it->second << "\n";
	it ++;
}
```

**结果：**

```
1 2
2 3
3 4
```



`mp.rbegin()`和`mp.rend()`
**用于逆向遍历map**

```cpp
map<int,int> mp;
mp[1] = 2;
mp[2] = 3;
mp[3] = 4;
auto it = mp.rbegin();
while(it != mp.rend())
{
	cout << it->first << " " << it->second << "\n";
	it ++;
}
```

**结果：**

```
3 4
2 3
1 2
```

